      "description": "Investment Managers Series Trust II - Tradr 2X Short AAOI Daily ETF is an exchange traded fund launched by Investment Managers Series Trust II. The fund is managed by AXS Investments LLC. It invests in public equity markets. The fund invests directly and invests through derivatives in stocks of companies operating across information technology, technology hardware and equipment, communications equipment, telephone and telecommunications equipment, communication services, telecommunication services sectors. The fund employs short strategy and uses derivatives such as swaps and options to create its portfolio. The fund invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified market capitalization. Investment Managers Series Trust II - Tradr 2X Short AAOI Daily ETF is domiciled in the United States.",
